window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Having just found her sister, Sofia temporarily becomes a summoner combat tactics professor at a prestigious magic academy?!</b></p> <p>Wait, this is still a book about skeletons, right? It is? Good.</p> <p>But can Sofia really spend an entire year in one place without causing chaos? We all know the answer to that already.</p> <p>What are the chances of her stealing the students' bones? Surely she would never!</p> <p>In a place home to so much knowledge, could she learn more about the mysteries of this world, the admins, and the Deep?</p> <p>It should have been a calm year, but with Sofia involved, the academy's higher-ups seem to be hiding something....</p>"; 
